'''Google, Inc.''' {{nasdaq|GOOG}}, is a [[United States|U.S.]]-based corporation, established in [[1998]], that manages the [[Google search]] engine. Google is headquartered at the "[[Googleplex]]" in [[Mountain View, Santa Clara County, California|Mountain View]], [[California]], and employs over 1,000 workers. [[Eric Schmidt|Dr. Eric Schmidt]] became Google's [[CEO]] (he was previously the CEO of [[Novell]]) when co-founder [[Lawrence E. Page|Larry Page]] stepped down.
